Best Basketball Player 2017-18

Eric Zirzow

November 28, 2017

Introduction

-Analyzed the current NBA season to try to predict the 2017-18 MVP

-Formula includes: Points, Rebounds, Assists, Steals, Blocks, Turnovers, and Shooting Percentage

Points

-Based off 20

-Weighted at 32.5%

Rebounds

-Based off 10

-Weighted at 20%

Assists

-Based off 10

-Weighted at 20%

Steals

-Based off 1.5

-Weighted at 10%

Blocks

-Based off 1.5

-Weighted at 10%

Additional Stats

-Turnovers based off 3, weighted at -10%

-FG shooting % based off 50%, weighted at 7.5%
